					.col.s12.m4
						.icon-block
							h2.center.teal-text
								i.material-icons favorite
							h5.center ใช้งานง่าย
							p.light
								| Mauris at metus et est elementum pulvinar sit amet at massa. Quisque non nulla imperdiet, vulputate lorem eget, condimentum
